vulnerabilities.title: Prototype Pollution in multi-ini
vulnerabilities.description: This affects the package multi-ini before 2.1.1. It is possible to pollute an object's prototype by specifying the proto object as part of an array.

vulnerabilities.title: Prototype pollution in multi-ini
vulnerabilities.description: This affects the package multi-ini before 2.1.2. It is possible to pollute an object's prototype by specifying the constructor.proto object as part of an array. This is a bypass of CVE-2020-28448.
